# PageSpeed Insights API key (optional).
# The `pagespeed` tool works keyless, but Google rate-limits anonymous requests.
# Set a free key (https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/v5/get-started)
# to raise the quota. Either variable name is accepted; PAGESPEED_API_KEY wins.
PAGESPEED_API_KEY=
# GOOGLE_PAGESPEED_API_KEY=
